sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant D as PostgreSQL
    participant C as Redis
    participant M as MongoDB

    Note over U,M: Rinovim Token — POST /auth/refresh

    U->>F: AccessToken skadoi (pas 15 minutave)
    F->>A: POST /auth/refresh (Cookie: refreshToken)
    A->>A: Lexo refreshToken nga cookie

    alt Cookie mungon
        A-->>F: 401 Token mungon
        F-->>U: Logohu sërisht
    else Cookie ekziston
        A->>A: Verifiko refreshToken
        alt RefreshToken i pavlefshëm
            A-->>F: 401 Token i pavlefshëm
            F-->>U: Logohu sërisht
        else RefreshToken i vlefshëm
            A->>D: Gjej userin
            D-->>A: User u gjet
            A->>A: Krijo accessToken të ri (15 min)
            A->>M: Regjistro rinovim
            A-->>F: 200 accessToken i ri
            F-->>U: Vazhdo sesionin
        end
    end

    Note over U,M: Logout — POST /auth/logout

    U->>F: Kliko "Dil"
    F->>A: POST /auth/logout (Bearer token)
    A->>A: Verifiko tokenin
    A->>C: Vendos tokenin në blacklist (900 sekonda)
    C-->>A: OK
    A->>M: Regjistro logout
    A-->>F: 200 U dil + Cookie fshihet
    F-->>U: Ridrejto te login